<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-0730-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: HISTORY'S MOBILE MOMENTS
 &HT;    Moving in the commentary (k) and national (a) categories.
 &HT;    Resending to fix transmission garbles.
 &HT;    For release Sunday, July 30.
