   SHARP-DRIVING _ ATLANTA _ Test driving a station wagon is not
normally something that would make my heart skip a beat. But I was
driving through the scenic rolling mountains of southern France.
The vehicle was Volvo's V70 wagon. My drive partner was He
Drove/She Drove's Paul Lienert. Paul tossed me the keys and assumed
