<P>
   BUSH-CHENEY (Austin, Texas) _ Texas Gov. George W. Bush and his
running mate Dick Cheney are planning a five-state tour on their
way to the Republican National Convention in Philadelphia. They
will visit Arkansas, Missouri, Kentucky, Ohio and West Virginia
before arriving in time to accept their party's nominations. By
STEWART M. POWELL.
</P>
