<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-27 14:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4633 &Cx1f; kan-z
r l BC-TRENDHYBRIDCARKANSAS-     07-27 1364
