   GARTH BROOKS-AUSTIN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Garth Brooks doing Garth Brooks _ and his rock-star
alter ego, Chris Gaines _ taped more than two hours' worth of music
for ``Austin City Limits'' last November; now the second half of
that evening _ a bunch of the hits, and two Gaines songs _ are
being shown this weekend on PBS. By DAVE FERMAN. Story has moved in
``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
