<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0725 _ A truly massive vehicle and one that's
ultra-sophisticated in some ways, the 2000 Lincoln Town Car also is
as retro as the 2001 Chrysler PT cruiser or any other vehicle
harkening to the good ol' days of cheap fuel and big-engined luxury
cars (DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes a
