<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-27 18:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4908 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u p BC-PELOSI-WHIP-HNS &LR;      07-27 0551
